   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00343"/><date>Sonntg</date></dateline></opener><p>Fand Euer ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>triges Telegra<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c> er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t abends, konnte er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t
               heute <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place">Bozen</rs> telegrafieren, erhielt dann Eure
               zweite Depe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che. Möchte <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00958-1"/>Mittwoch<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00958-1">Zum <date>16. 8. 1899</date> steht nichts
               in <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzlers</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb33243">Tagebuch</rs>.</note> er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ter Zug <rs ref="#pmb213" type="place">I<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chl</rs>
                  anko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en, Tag mit Ihnen verbringen, Rad mitnehmen,
               abends <rs ref="#pmb415" type="place">Au<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs> zurück, da ja <rs ref="#pmb10863" type="person">Richard</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00344"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00958-2"/><date>Do<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>erstag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb415" type="place">Au<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs> ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>t<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00958-2"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L00959" subtype="See"/>.</note>.</p><p>Vielleicht fahren wir zu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>a<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en <rs ref="#pmb39671" type="place">Hall<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tadt</rs>? oder Sie ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon
               Mittwoch <rs ref="#pmb415" type="place">Au<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs>? Aber was bei<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlechtem
               Wetter?</p><closer>Herzlich<lb/><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
